549
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:04,210
This is what my experience tells me.

550
00:39:04,210 --> 00:39:07,220
No matter what you'll need, I can satisfy you.

551
00:39:07,220 --> 00:39:10,120
You don't have to worry about any issue regarding globalization

552
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:12,850
because our company acquiring international companies

553
00:39:12,850 --> 00:39:16,130
is one of our strategies.

554
00:39:16,130 --> 00:39:18,150
Also, Cheng Yang,

555
00:39:18,910 --> 00:39:23,760
