556
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:26,280
I've also discussed it with our design department.

557
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:28,290
There is hope for you to carry Chinese elements

558
00:39:28,290 --> 00:39:32,040
from ourselves to the international stage.

559
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:35,240
Through our collaboration, I further hope

560
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:40,400
